(378, 1, '2017-12-11 06:43:09', '2017-12-11 06:43:09', 'PEANUT BUTTER CUPCAKES AND FILLING\r\n\r\n1/2 cup (104g) sugar\r\n1/4 cup (45g) lightly packed light brown sugar\r\n¼ cup (56g) unsalted butter, room temperature\r\n½ cup (140g) peanut butter\r\n¼ cup (60ml/58g) sour cream, room temperature\r\n1 tsp vanilla extract\r\n3 large egg whites, room temperature, lightly beaten\r\n1 1/4 cups (163g) all purpose flour\r\n2 tsp baking powder\r\n¼ tsp salt\r\n6 tbsp (90ml) milk, room temperature\r\n2 tbsp (30ml) water, room temperature\r\n1 cup marshmallow cream/fluff\r\n\r\n\r\nNUTELLA FROSTING\r\n\r\n1/2 cup (84g) butter\r\n1/4 cup (36g) shortening\r\n1/2 cup (157g) Nutella\r\n4 1/2 cups (518g) powdered sugar\r\n4 1/2 tbsp water or cream\r\nLarge marshmallows ,', 'Nutella Fluffernutter Cupcake', 'Nutella Fluffernutter Cupcakes are a moist peanut butter cupcake filled with marshmallow fluff and topped with Nutella frosting! They remind me of one of my favorite sandwiches as a kid – and they are definitely just as delicious!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://www.lifeloveandsugar.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Nutella-Fluffernutter-Cupcakes1.jpg', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nutella-fluffernutter-cupcake', '', '', '2017-12-11 06:43:09', '2017-12-11 06:43:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=378', 0, 'product', '', 0);
