(479, 1, '2017-12-11 08:52:28', '2017-12-11 08:52:28', '<strong>Cake can help you slim</strong>\r\n\r\nIsh… You do have to eat it in the morning though, not your usual afternoon tea slot. Because a study a few years ago showed eating a dessert as part of a balanced 600-calorie breakfast helped dieters lose weight, with a lower chance of piling the pounds back on than those who were not having a sneaky breakfast pudding. It’s all about metabolism early in the day being more active than later.', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '479', '', '', '2017-12-11 08:52:28', '2017-12-11 08:52:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=479', 0, 'post', '', 0),
